                        <interp inst="t18781021-905-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">of receiving; she also</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">

PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to a previous conviction at the Westminster Sessions on 2nd September</hi>, 1877.**—<hi rend="italic">

